      <h2 class="display-5 fw-bold text-primary">About Medulance</h2>
      <p class="lead">Medulance Healthcare is a pioneering medical emergency service provider offering a comprehensive range of emergency and non-emergency ambulance services. Our fleet is equipped with the latest medical technology and staffed by highly trained medical professionals, ensuring the highest standards of care for our patients.</p>

      <h3 class="mt-4">Our History</h3>
      <p class="lead">Founded in 2015, Medulance began with a mission to revolutionize medical emergency response services in India. Starting with a small fleet, we have grown exponentially over the years, expanding our services across multiple cities and regions. Our commitment to rapid response and quality care has made us a trusted name in emergency medical services.</p>

      <h3 class="mt-4">Current Services</h3>
      <ul class="lead">
        <li><strong>Emergency Ambulance:</strong> Provides immediate medical assistance and transport for patients in critical conditions requiring urgent medical attention. These ambulances are equipped with Advanced Life Support (ALS) systems and trained medical personnel to handle emergencies such as heart attacks, strokes, severe injuries, and other life-threatening situations.</li>
        <li><strong>Non-Emergency Ambulance:</strong> Offers transportation for patients who require medical assistance but are not in immediate danger. These services are ideal for routine hospital visits, patient transfers, and transportation to medical appointments.</li>
        <li><strong>Air Ambulance:</strong> Provides rapid medical transport for critically ill patients who need to be transported over long distances or to specialized medical facilities. Our air ambulances are equipped with state-of-the-art medical equipment and staffed by experienced medical professionals.</li>
        <li><strong>Telemedicine:</strong> Connects patients with medical professionals through digital platforms, offering consultations, follow-ups, and medical advice without the need for physical visits. This service enhances accessibility and convenience for patients, especially in remote areas.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="mt-4">Future Advancements</h3>
      <p class="lead">At Medulance, we are constantly innovating to improve our services and meet the evolving needs of our patients. Our future plans include:</p>
      <ul class="lead">
        <li>Expanding our fleet with more advanced ambulances equipped with cutting-edge medical technology.</li>
        <li>Implementing AI-powered systems for better route optimization and faster response times.</li>
        <li>Enhancing our telemedicine services with more interactive and user-friendly platforms.</li>
        <li>Collaborating with more hospitals and healthcare providers to offer integrated and seamless medical services.</li>
        <li>Launching community outreach programs to educate the public about emergency preparedness and first aid.</li>
      </ul>
